11 An Act relating to motor vehicles; amending 47 O.S.
2021, Section 12-609, which relates to required
12 equipment for motorcycles; deleting limitation on the
height of motorcycle handlebars; and providing an
13 effective date.
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 47 O.S. 2021, Section 12-609, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 12-609. A. In addition to other requirements
20 prescribed by this chapter, by federal law or by local ordinance,
21 all motorcycles, except when operated on actual trail rides
22 conducted outside of public roads and highways, shall be equipped
23 with:
24
